&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 56w: check lfs_migrate -c stripe_count works == 18:28:50 (1357784930)
/usr/bin/lfs_migrate -y -c 6 /mnt/lustre/d0.sanity/d56w/file1
/usr/bin/lfs_migrate: line 100: /bin: is a directory
